        "code": { "language": "plaintext", "showLineNumbers": false },
        "content": "## Dashboard qo'llanmasi\n\n### RED metrikalar (yuqori)\nStandart observability layout: **Rate** (throughput), **Errors** (%), **Duration** (p95), plus p50/p95/p99 latency chart.\n\n### Trace jadvallar\n| Jadval | TraceQL | Ma'nosi |\n|--------|---------|--------|\n| **Xato tracelar** | `{status=error}` | faqat error trace |\n| **Sekin tracelar** | `{duration>1s}` | 1 soniyadan uzoq |\n| **So'nggi tracelar** | `{}` | hammasi (sampled) |\n\nDuration ustuni: **yashil** <1s · **sariq** 1–3s · **qizil** >3s\n\n### Test\n```\nInvoke-WebRequest http://localhost:8080/api/products\nInvoke-WebRequest \"http://localhost:8080/api/slow?ms=2000\"\nInvoke-WebRequest \"http://localhost:8080/api/error?code=500\"\n```\n\nJaeger: http://localhost:16686 · Coroot: http://localhost:8082"
